default4.default              defaultVariations on Option 2default&#xa0;
default4.1
default              
defaultThe 
defaultCEA does not be
defaultlieve that Option 2 should be pursued.  If the Government wishes to explore deregulation of community-based film exhibition further, we would be happy to contribute.  However, it should not be the case that the sector must work to the arbitrary timetable o
defaultf the current draft Deregulation Bill.  It is more important to reach safe and robust decisions than to reach rapid ones.
